item.title: whoami
item.description: [ouranos@manjaro ~]$ whoami Hey, i'm Mohamed a cyber security student, passionate about everything related to low level programming, my strongest skills lie within: binary exploitation, desktop app programming, reverse engineering. Also i have a lot of skills that need to be sharpened more like web programming and system administration. Here are the technologies that i work with : Programming langs : C/C++, python, bash Frameworks : Flask, QT, django Tools : git, docker, gdb, ghidra, vmware.
